headline: Hippocratic AI Raises $126 Million in Series C at $3.5 Billion Valuation Led by Avenir Growth to Expand Clinically Safe Generative AI Agents Across Healthcare
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., November 03, 2025--Hippocratic AI closed its Series C financing, raising $126 million at a $3.5 billion valuation and bringing its total funding to $404 million.
